## Write a program to find area of a rectangle

Area of rectangle = `Length` × `Width`

```
Length : 2
Width  : 3

Area : 6
```

---

<CodeBlock slug="find-area-of-a-rectangle" >

```c
#include <stdio.h>

int main(){

    int length, width, area;  
    printf("Enter length\n");
    scanf("%d", &length);
    printf("Enter width\n");
    scanf("%d", &width);

    area = length * width;
    printf("Area = %d\n", area);
    return 0;
}
```

